{
  "stem": "3097.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he got caught there, while doing it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They took him on the Jewish cemetery, and they killed him there, and he's married-- buried on the Jewish cemetery, this Kozubek.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Czerwiec. ?] I lost [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Czerwiec, ?] too, because [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Czerwiec ?] was supposed to get the order that he is supposed to go to Romania, from Romania to Italy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Whatever happened to him, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we are left without those two people, by the end.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I decided, again, to try to force through to the more positive groups which could help us out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I made contact with somebody who said-- he said, somebody there in Daleszyce, in a-- in a village, who has contact with the peasants' army.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went there-- knocked on the door.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A woman opened, and the man was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I told them what it is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, yes, I know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, what do you want?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, we want to make contact with the Armia Ludowa.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, he said, I know what it is, you see.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let me take you to the forest, and we'll make-- I call another man with me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We'll go to-- to the bunker.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they went like that, without anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They went there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they put it in a bunker.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a little hill, and there was a deep bunker.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they say, you wait here, and we'll come to get-- make contact with you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, when they left, those two guys left, I said to Wasser, who was with me, I said, you know, I'm suspicious.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know what they know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, you know what?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Let's go back, behind the trees, and see what happens.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
